<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12828] Add getTableAttributes API to HBaseAdmin class. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12828</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;At present, there is no api/function to get table attributes. It would be nice to have a function that returns table attributes given the table name.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
